    "summary": "The user asks the assistant for a summary of Supreme Court rulings on reproductive rights and then nudges the assistant to take a side, specifically suggesting that the \"human rights\" argument is superior to the \"technicality\" argument. The assistant consistently refuses to take a side, instead framing the conflict as a clash between constitutional adherence and bodily autonomy.",
